header.gameNote: ACC/BIG TEN CHALLENGE PRES. BY LG V20

videos.description: Grayson Allen is ready for the spotlight as he hits an early 3-pointer for Duke to get the Cameron Crazies fired up.
videos.headline: Allen's 3-pointer ignites Cameron Crazies

videos.description: 1H (12:14) MSU Nick Ward made Dunk. Assisted by Cassius Winston.
videos.headline: Michigan State fastbreak leads to Ward dunk

videos.description: Michigan State gets running down the court after a made basket leaves Kenny Goins open for a huge two-handed slam that quiets the Cameron Crazies.
videos.headline: Massive dunk has Goins screaming, Crazies silent
Jeter dunk after the missed Duke 3-pointer

videos.description: 1H (4:45) MSU Joshua Langford made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Langford hits the 3-pointer from the top of the key

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo discusses ball movement in 1st half
videos.headline: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo discusses ball movement in 1st half

videos.description: 2H (10:20) MSU Matt McQuaid made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Lourawls Nairn Jr..
videos.headline: McQuaid knocks down the 3-pointer for Michigan State

videos.description: Michigan State's Miles Bridges throws the ball back in play right to Grayson Allen, and while he misses his shot, Frank Jackson gets the second look and drains the 3-pointer to increase Duke's lead.
videos.headline: Duke getting to the loose ball results in Blue Devils' 3-pointer

videos.description: 2H (3:06) DUKE Grayson Allen made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Frank Jackson.
videos.headline: Allen hits the long range 3-pointer

videos.description: Off the missed shot, Miles Bridges leaps over everyone for the ridiculous putback dunk.
videos.headline: Bridges soars over everyone for putback dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen says his team's defense was the key against Michigan State as it was able to jump start Duke's offense at the other end in a 78-69 win.
videos.headline: Allen says Duke's defense started Duke's offense
